NG0275:1: gang bsgral ba la'ang glang po che dang */

NG0275:491: kha kha mu kha bya rog gdong *//
NG0275:492: khros pa'i sems kyi rab sbyar na //

NG0275:505: mtshungs rgyu slob ma nyid la gnas //

NG0275:541: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' mchod //
